>\n例如對象係中共fans 就講港英餘孽去argue<br />\n例如對象係港豬就屌醒佢<br />\n不過當然你自己首先要好了解成個修正案利弊<br />\n可以既話都了解下中共以往既人權爭議案 67暴動 黃背心 <br />\n順便長下知識<br />\n<br />\n另外比較急切既應該係增加遊行人數<br />\n直接問叫身邊既人一齊去啦 <br />\n可能佢仲猶豫緊 <br />\n可能佢上次冇去有後悔 <br />\n可能佢因為冇FD陪而唔去<br />\n可能佢過左經過左呢個星期改變左立場<br />\n<br />\n又或者打開whatsapp搵下d沉底group 約下人星期日gathering 可能有意外收穫<br />\n當然亦可以參與派傳單 po多幾個ig story <br />\n<br />\n有人話香港有600萬人支持修訂逃犯條例<br />\n多謝佢地提醒我地其實仲有好多潛在同伴<br />\n其實只要每人可以說服多一個人出黎，616就可能見到206萬人<br />\n呀 諗起都扯扯地<br />\n<br />\n以上只係好表面諗到既野<br />\n希望各位巴絲可以一齊組織下同諗辦法"},{"pid":"6fcdd1b6b3be011ac7d9abca1f2f99367b454c55","tid":1223446,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmlyc6%2Fvideos%2F2413922815343553%2F&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8Ab0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=9a2f35d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/</a>"},{"pid":"2f77f5c6384d05ead876aa98aa20f3c09dd0e81f","tid":1223446,"uid":253170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fcdd1b6b3be011ac7d9abca1f2f99367b454c55","tid":1223446,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmlyc6%2Fvideos%2F2413922815343553%2F&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8Ab0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=9a2f35d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:46:00.000Z","msg":"白色衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850fac38374c2339b70f08db8b656af1889dd20a","tid":1223446,"uid":22764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"成功叫醒左身邊d 港豬fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla